            "post_author_verified": false,
            "post_time": "14h ago",
            "post_text": "<p>i've been wearing this ring every day for about a month now and honestly it's become part of my routine. i mainly got it to keep an eye on my sleep and activity levels, but i ended up checking my recovery and heart rate almost every morning. it's comfortable enough that i forget i'm wearing it.<br/><br/></p>",
