      "blocks": {
        "faq_wrist_1": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Can I Wear It All Day And Night?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely. Trainixy™ is lightweight, comfortable, and designed for continuous wear, whether you're working, exercising, relaxing, or sleeping.<br/><br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_wrist_2": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Will The Ring Help Me Understand My Health Better?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. By tracking trends in sleep, activity, heart rate, and recovery, Trainixy™ helps you better understand your daily habits and make more informed wellness decisions.<br/><br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_wrist_3": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Does The App Show Historical Data?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. The companion app stores your health and activity history, allowing you to review daily, weekly, and monthly trends over time.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_wrist_4": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Is This Ring Suitable For Men And Women?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely. Trainixy™ features a minimalist unisex design that looks great on any hand and fits a wide range of lifestyles.<br/><br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_wrist_5": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Why Are More People Switching To Smart Rings?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Smart rings offer many of the benefits of wearable technology while being smaller, more discreet, and easier to wear throughout the day. They're ideal for people who want health insights without constantly checking a screen.<br/><br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_wrist_6": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "What colors are available?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Available in White, Black and Pink. </p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_wrist_7": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "What if I'm not happy with the product?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>We offer a 90-day money-back guarantee. If you use it consistently and are not satisfied with your experience for any reason, reach out to our team and we will make it right — no questions asked.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        }
